        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nHi,\n\nThis commit aims to extract the checkArtifactInComponent and checkArtifactInResourceInstance functions from the ArtifactsBusinessLogic class to shrink it a bit. Tests have been added along with some utility functions designed to generate randomized test data. The former tests were deleted as they were not doing any assertions and relied on reflection which is discouraged by Java 11.\n\nThanks in advance for your help,\n\nFrancis.",
